rip within steps of the most popular restaurants, shops and night life that Los Angeles has to offer and within minutes of the area’s many galleries, museums and local business communities.  Nestled between Beverly Hills and Hollywood, Mondrian’s location is the ideal hub to access numerous area attractions such as Sunset Plaza, The Beverly Center, Melrose and Santa Monica Boulevards, Hollywood Walk of Fame, Mann’s Chinese Theater, Kodak Theater, Getty Center, UCLA and world class shopping on renowned Rodeo Drive.</p><a href="http://www.hotelrooms.com/Brand_Ian_Schrager_Hotels_Los_Angeles.htm">Los Angeles Hotel Reservations</a><a href="http://http://www.tablethotels.com/Hotel/en/304/Review/The-Mondrian-Hotel/Los-Angeles-California-United-States">Morgans Hotel Reservations</a></noscript></span><!-- Main Nav --><div id="lowerhomenav"><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="8" width="5" /><br /><div class="homenav"><span class="nav"><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com"><img src="images/MHGgray.gif" alt="Morgans Hotel Group" width="180" height="12" border="0"/></a><br /><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt="" height="3" width="5" /><br /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com" title="Morgans Hotel Group Home Page">Home</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/reserve.asp" title="Online Reservations">Reservations</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/hotels.asp" title="Hotels">Hotels</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/meetings.asp"  title="Meetings and Events Services">Meetings &amp; Events</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.morganshotelgroup.com/play.asp"  title="Party Pictures, City Guides and Unique Mailers">Play</a><img src="images/spacer.gif" alt=""  width="7" height="4" /><a href="http://www.